.</p> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Which, historically, was fine. The othe=
r essential fact about private companies was, for a long time, that their s=
tock didn=E2=80=99t trade. Public companies had publicly traded stock; priv=
ate companies did not have traded stock. People who owned stock in private =
companies could not regularly sell it, so there wasn=E2=80=99t too much rea=
son to worry about insider trading.</p> <p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Now, t=
